snippet.title: Alien Hell for the Atari 8-bit family
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

???


Game description:

Alien Hell is an Adventure game in which you have to go through many different areas where either aliens or other obstacles await you.


What I think:

Nice game. A little bit atmospheric too.
